<div id="preamble"><h1>Apache モジュール mod_auth_basic</h1>
<div class="toplang">
<p><span>Available Languages: </span><a href="../en/mod/mod_auth_basic.html" hreflang="en" rel="alternate" title="English">&nbsp;en&nbsp;</a> |
